race.description: Wangaratta Cup - On Sale Now (Bm62) Handicap
race.comment: GEE TEE (12) resumes for a leading stable and was last seen at Stakes level over 1800m. He's proven fresh and won a recent jumpout. Has an awkward barrier but Coffey is booked suggesting she's ready to go. TORN (3) is third-up with more to give. Has an inside gate and McDougall replaces the 3kg apprentice. He will get every chance. EN FLIQUE (13) has jumped out well since last seen and would be a hope finding his best form. SEEYOU RAIDER (5) bounced back to form last start with a much better performance at Yarra Valley. Would've taken great confidence from that effort and the rating there stacks up. Keep safe.
